  <!-- ============================================================
       OVERVIEW SECTION
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="section section--white" aria-label="Product overview">
    <div class="container product-overview">
      <div class="product-overview__text">
        <span class="section-eyebrow">What It Is</span>
        <h2 class="h2">ITF Certified Acrylic Surfacing for Professional Play</h2>
        <span class="section-divider" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <p>Our 100% acrylic sports court systems are designed to provide consistent pace of play, vibrant colors, and long-lasting durability against harsh UV rays and heavy usage.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:1rem;">Available in both hard court (3 to 5 layers) and cushioned (upto 8 layers) configurations, acrylic surfacing is the standard for professional tennis courts worldwide, providing excellent slip resistance and true ball bounce characteristics.</p>
        <div class="product-overview__tags" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
          <span class="pac-tag">True Ball Bounce</span>
          <span class="pac-tag">Highly Customizable</span>
          <span class="pac-tag">UV &amp; Weather Resistant</span>
          <span class="pac-tag">ITF Certified</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="product-overview__img">
        <img src="/images/gallery-acrylic-closeup.png" alt="Close-up of textured acrylic court surface" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="section section--white" aria-label="Technical specifications">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <h2 class="h2">Technical Specifications</h2>
        <span class="section-divider" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="specs-table-wrap reveal">
        <table class="specs-table">
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="specs-table__key">Material</td>
              <td class="specs-table__val">100% Pure Acrylic Resin &amp; Pigments</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="specs-table__key">System Types</td>
              <td class="specs-table__val">Hard Court (Standard) / Cushion Court (Rubber infused)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="specs-table__key">Sub-base Requirement</td>
              <td class="specs-table__val">Properly cured concrete (with vapor barrier) or asphalt</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="specs-table__key">Surface Texture</td>
              <td class="specs-table__val">Silica sand infused for precise slip resistance</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="specs-table__key">UV Resistance</td>
              <td class="specs-table__val">High - Colors resist fading under strong sunlight</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="specs-table__key">Application Method</td>
              <td class="specs-table__val">Squeegee applied in multiple successive layers</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="specs-table__key">Pace / Speed</td>
              <td class="specs-table__val">Adjustable (ITF Category 1 to 5) based on sand grading</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       WHY CHOOSE
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="section section--surface" aria-label="Why choose Acrylic Systems">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <h2 class="h2">Why Choose Acrylic Court Systems</h2>
        <span class="section-divider" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-card reveal">
          <div class="why-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="why-card__title">True Ball Bounce</h3>
          <p>The seamless, monolithic surface provides identical ball bounce across the entire court, which is critical for professional tennis and basketball.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="why-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="why-card__title">Customizable Pace</h3>
          <p>By adjusting the silica sand mixture, we can precisely tune the surface speed from slow to fast, matching ITF specifications.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="why-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="why-card__title">Vibrant Aesthetics</h3>
          <p>100% acrylic pigments provide deep, rich colors that completely transform the look of a facility and resist fading for years.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

